HEADWORD: Prayerless
<hw>Prayer"less</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not using
prayer; habitually neglecting prayer to God; without prayer.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧The next time you go <xex>prayerless</xex> to bed.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Baxter.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

